= Episode 22 =

11
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:43,830
Tonghao is kind

12
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,270
and smart.

13
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:48,830
He loves helping others.

14
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:53,190
At first, he helped me deliver goods,

15
00:01:54,310 --> 00:01:56,120
and then he did all the heavy labor.

16
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,360
Later,

17
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:00,870
he assisted us in managing the inn.

18
00:02:03,230 --> 00:02:05,000
He was meticulous about details,

19
00:02:06,550 --> 00:02:08,800
such as the napkin folding,

20
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:10,320
tableware arrangement

21
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:12,160
and floor cleaning.

22
00:02:13,750 --> 00:02:14,910
Other than that,

23
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:18,160
he’s friendly to everyone.

24
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,720
We all like him.

25
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:23,750
Tonghao said

26
00:02:24,910 --> 00:02:26,440
this is his home

27
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:29,630
and the place he desires to protect.

28
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:36,080
He’s the most adorable person

29
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,880
I’ve ever seen.

30
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:57,030
This is the first time you brought him up

31
00:02:58,440 --> 00:02:59,800
and probably the last time.

32
00:03:01,390 --> 00:03:02,750
Can you give me a minute?

33
00:03:04,190 --> 00:03:04,880
No.

34
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:06,910
Ten seconds are enough.

35
00:03:09,190 --> 00:03:11,000
Just pretend you’re Tonghao.

36
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:31,470
Why?

37
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,960
Because I miss him a lot.

38
00:03:48,500 --> 00:03:49,520
I didn’t even get to

39
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,080
say goodbye to him properly.

40
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:34,670
I’m not Tonghao.

41
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:48,200
Shan Junhao,

42
00:05:48,620 --> 00:05:49,350
you should leave.

43
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:40,320
Yunyi.

44
00:06:41,230 --> 00:06:41,720
Ziqian.

45
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:43,600
Don’t say anything.

46
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:44,670
Yunyi.

47
00:07:46,670 --> 00:07:47,350
Are you OK?

48
00:07:48,670 --> 00:07:50,040
Are you not feeling well?

49
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,790
I’m fine, Mom.

50
00:08:00,140 --> 00:08:03,440
You look spiritless since you came back.

51
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:05,950
What happened?

52
00:08:06,350 --> 00:08:08,160
You can tell me.

53
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:13,040
Mom, you’re still up?

54
00:08:16,300 --> 00:08:18,230
Why are you dressed up like this?

55
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:21,760
Why did you get that outfit?

56
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:23,000
And your hair.

57
00:08:23,390 --> 00:08:24,830
What happened?

58
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:28,160
I got wet by accident.

59
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,160
There were no other clothes available

60
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,510
but only these.

61
00:08:31,510 --> 00:08:32,440
Junhao,

62
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:35,000
is your work all done?

63
00:08:39,550 --> 00:08:40,230
Yes.

64
00:08:42,150 --> 00:08:43,110
Junhao,

65
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:45,320
you’re still lying to me!

66
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,520
Your lie pains me more

67
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:49,230
than seeing you and Ye Qianyu hug.

68
00:08:50,110 --> 00:08:50,960
What?

69
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:55,000
You went to see that woman?

70
00:09:01,550 --> 00:09:02,150
Yunyi,

71
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,670
you mistook it.

72
00:09:04,550 --> 00:09:06,200
It’s not what you think.

73
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:08,110
Nothing is going on between us.

74
00:09:08,110 --> 00:09:10,840
I saw it myself. Don’t deny it!

75
00:09:11,110 --> 00:09:13,400
You promised to watch the meteor shower with me,

76
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:15,150
yet you went to see her behind my back.

77
00:09:15,150 --> 00:09:16,670
How could you do that to me?

78
00:09:16,670 --> 00:09:17,840
I told you

79
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,670
we’re clean.

80
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:21,150
Why didn’t you believe me?

81
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:22,880
She forced me

82
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:24,400
to be Tonghao for ten seconds.

83
00:09:26,550 --> 00:09:29,470
Know the look in your eyes when she hugged you?

84
00:09:32,230 --> 00:09:33,470
Your eyes

85
00:09:34,230 --> 00:09:35,790
already gave you away.

86
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,470
Is what she said

87
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:48,520
all true?

88
00:09:51,470 --> 00:09:53,350
Do not go see her again!

89
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:21,080
Tonghao is kind and smart.

90
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:22,590
He’s the most adorable person

91
00:10:23,670 --> 00:10:24,880
I’ve ever seen.

92
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:39,590
This is the first time you brought him up

93
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:42,400
and probably the last time.

94
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:45,110
Can you give me a minute?

95
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:47,500
No.

96
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,280
Ten seconds are enough.

97
00:10:51,520 --> 00:10:53,280
Just pretend you’re Tonghao.

98
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,080
Hi, Yunyi.

99
00:12:00,910 --> 00:12:01,590
Dawei.

100
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:03,200
I’ll drive to work myself.

101
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:22,860
Mr. Shan.

102
00:12:23,110 --> 00:12:24,760
Yunyi said she’ll drive herself today.

103
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:30,280
Let’s go.

104
00:12:57,230 --> 00:12:57,790
Junhao,

105
00:12:59,220 --> 00:13:00,790
why didn’t Yunyi come with you?

106
00:13:08,910 --> 00:13:10,440
Why are you here so early?

107
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:12,400
I have an appointment

108
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:13,670
with someone.

109
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:17,380
Junhao,

110
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:21,320
if you don’t cherish Yunyi,

111
00:13:22,910 --> 00:13:23,790
someone else will.

112
00:13:25,910 --> 00:13:26,880
But you can’t hurt her.

113
00:13:28,030 --> 00:13:29,320
Yunyi is my fiancée.

114
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:31,080
Why would I hurt her?

115
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:33,110
I thought you forgot who she is.

116
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:36,000
Since we were little,

117
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:39,080
have you ever truly cared for anyone

118
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:40,000
even for a minute?

119
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:54,640
Let’s go.

120
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:55,550
Yes.

121
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:06,280
Come in.

122
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:08,960
Here are the files you asked for, Mr. Shan.

123
00:14:11,110 --> 00:14:12,400
I’ll put them on your table.

124
00:14:17,110 --> 00:14:18,930
If there’s nothing else,

125
00:14:18,930 --> 00:14:19,830
I’ll be out.

126
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:26,280
You really think I don’t care

127
00:14:26,280 --> 00:14:27,800
about anyone around me?

128
00:14:29,760 --> 00:14:32,150
Uh, Mr. Shan,

129
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:34,400
are you asking me?

130
00:14:34,670 --> 00:14:35,640
Who else is here?

131
00:14:35,640 --> 00:14:37,470
Is there anyone else in this room?

132
00:14:39,230 --> 00:14:40,320
Mr. Shan,

133
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:42,030
you never need others’ advice,

134
00:14:42,320 --> 00:14:44,440
so I’m not used to this.

135
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:46,320
What should I do

136
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:49,320
to cheer a girl up?

137
00:14:55,150 --> 00:14:57,760
Never mind. You have no girlfriend.

138
00:14:57,760 --> 00:14:59,200
Asking you is of no use.

139
00:15:00,150 --> 00:15:01,000
Well,

140
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:03,710
it’s true that I’m single,

141
00:15:04,110 --> 00:15:05,790
but I know a thing or two

142
00:15:05,790 --> 00:15:07,520
about dating.

143
00:15:07,960 --> 00:15:08,670
Mr. Shan,

144
00:15:09,350 --> 00:15:13,910
when you’re with Miss Fan, you’re a bit...

145
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:17,730
A bit what?

146
00:15:20,030 --> 00:15:20,940
Mr. Shan,

147
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:22,790
with all due respect,

148
00:15:23,350 --> 00:15:25,590
you’re a typical straight man.

149
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:26,910
Girls

150
00:15:27,150 --> 00:15:29,550
want you to spend more time with them,

151
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:30,880
drive them everywhere,

152
00:15:30,880 --> 00:15:33,000
and share joys and sorrows with them.

153
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,910
Make sure they can reach you 24/7.

154
00:15:35,280 --> 00:15:36,440
Just like how you treat me?

155
00:15:36,590 --> 00:15:37,880
No, Mr. Shan,

156
00:15:37,880 --> 00:15:38,910
I don’t like you.

157
00:15:41,350 --> 00:15:43,350
No, uh, I don’t like men.

158
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:45,840
No, I mean...

159
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:47,350
My point is

160
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:49,200
girls

161
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:53,080
need care and romance.

162
00:15:53,350 --> 00:15:54,200
For example,

163
00:15:54,670 --> 00:15:57,110
you can say more sweet words,

164
00:15:57,440 --> 00:16:01,030
and give them small surprises.

165
00:16:01,550 --> 00:16:02,960
If you two argue,

166
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:04,320
no matter who’s at fault,

167
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:06,320
you should apologize immediately.

168
00:16:06,790 --> 00:16:08,230
Kneel, if necessary.

169
00:16:08,230 --> 00:16:09,470
Don’t just stand there.

170
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:11,080
Anyway,

171
00:16:11,280 --> 00:16:11,880
remember one thing,

172
00:16:12,230 --> 00:16:12,760
spoil them.

173
00:16:18,550 --> 00:16:23,880
How should I make small surprises?

174
00:16:25,710 --> 00:16:26,460
Sir,

175
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:28,880
you’re asking the right person.

176
00:16:30,590 --> 00:16:31,550
There are many ways.

177
00:16:32,470 --> 00:16:33,550
For instance,

178
00:16:33,550 --> 00:16:37,080
prepare a special gift in secret

179
00:16:37,710 --> 00:16:40,880
and ask her out to a romantic place,

180
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:44,710
then surprise her.

181
00:16:45,910 --> 00:16:47,470
Will it work?

182
00:16:47,470 --> 00:16:48,080
Of course.

183
00:16:48,590 --> 00:16:50,110
It’ll work like a charm.

184
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,840
Mr. Shan, if that’s all,

185
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:58,840
I’ll go back to work.

186
00:17:10,430 --> 00:17:12,310
Princess Snow

187
00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:14,160
is really something.

188
00:17:14,350 --> 00:17:15,280
Her previous videos

189
00:17:15,280 --> 00:17:17,560
only received millions of hits.

190
00:17:18,040 --> 00:17:20,680
But since she posted that photo with Shan Junhao,

191
00:17:21,160 --> 00:17:23,040
her fan base and popularity

192
00:17:23,040 --> 00:17:24,640
have grown dramatically.

193
00:17:25,310 --> 00:17:27,040
She’s so good at promoting herself.

194
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:29,070
But then again,

195
00:17:29,350 --> 00:17:31,310
Shan Junhao made a huge sacrifice

196
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:32,760
for our inn.

197
00:17:33,190 --> 00:17:35,640
He never took photos with others,

198
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:37,070
but this time,

199
00:17:37,070 --> 00:17:39,000
he made an exception for us

200
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:40,920
and agreed to let Princess Snow post it online.

201
00:17:41,590 --> 00:17:43,280
I could also do that

202
00:17:43,280 --> 00:17:44,470
for Guanmei.

203
00:17:44,470 --> 00:17:45,880
Oh, save it!

204
00:17:45,880 --> 00:17:47,880
If you change your WeChat photo,

205
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:49,590
maybe more girls will friend you.

206
00:17:49,590 --> 00:17:51,710
I don’t want other girls.

207
00:17:52,230 --> 00:17:53,520
Liyin,

208
00:17:53,520 --> 00:17:55,040
can you get me out

209
00:17:55,040 --> 00:17:56,110
from the blocked list?

210
00:17:56,430 --> 00:17:58,560
I’ve been massaging your shoulders for so long.

211
00:17:59,710 --> 00:18:02,800
If you continue to massage my arms,

212
00:18:02,800 --> 00:18:04,640
I’ll grant your request.

213
00:18:05,430 --> 00:18:06,100
Deal.

214
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:09,430
This time, not only didn’t Shan Junhao

215
00:18:10,070 --> 00:18:12,520
destroy our inn,

216
00:18:12,520 --> 00:18:13,880
but he helped us instead.

217
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:16,470
Sometimes, I feel as if

218
00:18:16,920 --> 00:18:18,520
Tonghao were back.

219
00:18:19,760 --> 00:18:20,830
Perhaps

220
00:18:21,110 --> 00:18:23,800
Tonghao is inside his heart.

221
00:18:24,280 --> 00:18:26,160
Thanks to him,

222
00:18:26,430 --> 00:18:29,470
all the other media

223
00:18:29,470 --> 00:18:31,680
won’t publish Princess Snow’s allergy incident.

224
00:18:33,560 --> 00:18:34,280
But,

225
00:18:34,280 --> 00:18:36,070
when we host events like this in the future,

226
00:18:36,070 --> 00:18:37,470
we should be more careful.

227
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:39,520
Yes.

228
00:18:39,800 --> 00:18:41,880
Senwell has recognized Guanmei Inn

229
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:43,350
as part of its group.

230
00:18:43,520 --> 00:18:44,710
It’s a good thing

231
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:46,310
and it also means

232
00:18:46,710 --> 00:18:47,800
Guanmei Inn is temporarily free from the risk

233
00:18:47,800 --> 00:18:49,430
of being leveled.

234
00:18:51,710 --> 00:18:53,920
I guess that’s our biggest gain

235
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:54,800
from this event.

236
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:57,470
Alright.

237
00:18:58,470 --> 00:19:00,000
That’s all for the summary.

238
00:19:00,430 --> 00:19:01,590
It’s time to relax.

239
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:03,830
Relax?

240
00:19:10,950 --> 00:19:11,470
It’s weird.

241
00:19:12,230 --> 00:19:13,160
How come Fengqiao and Sheng

242
00:19:13,160 --> 00:19:14,920
didn’t come downstairs?

243
00:19:17,950 --> 00:19:19,800
I’m going to the Money Bag Grocery.

244
00:19:20,310 --> 00:19:21,070
You two take your time.

245
00:19:25,280 --> 00:19:28,040
How should we relax?

246
00:19:42,190 --> 00:19:42,880
What are you doing here?

247
00:19:43,430 --> 00:19:44,710
To buy toothpaste.

248
00:19:48,280 --> 00:19:51,350
Doesn’t the inn have a toothpaste supplier?

249
00:19:52,110 --> 00:19:53,310
Why did you come here to buy it?

250
00:19:54,590 --> 00:19:55,110
Speak!

251
00:19:56,560 --> 00:19:58,640
Did you do something dirty

252
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:01,400
while I was away?

253
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:02,590
Of course not.

254
00:20:03,590 --> 00:20:04,760
I didn’t do anything.

255
00:20:15,110 --> 00:20:15,780
Uh...

256
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:18,110
Where is this bouquet from?

257
00:20:18,110 --> 00:20:19,190
Butterball,

258
00:20:19,190 --> 00:20:21,000
did you see anyone here?

259
00:20:21,470 --> 00:20:22,760
No.

260
00:20:22,760 --> 00:20:24,710
Not even a fly.

261
00:20:24,710 --> 00:20:25,800
Who put it here?

262
00:20:25,800 --> 00:20:29,430
Did Taichu buy it for Qianyu?

263
00:20:29,430 --> 00:20:29,860
Don’t think so.

264
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:31,190
They went out together.

265
00:20:32,280 --> 00:20:36,230
Could it be a gift for me from Li Donglu?

266
00:20:37,520 --> 00:20:40,110
Behave yourself and act your age!

267
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:41,000
Would Li Donglu

268
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,830
be so generous?

269
00:20:42,830 --> 00:20:44,160
At least, he’s better than you.

270
00:20:45,280 --> 00:20:47,800
I’m old and attractive.

271
00:20:47,800 --> 00:20:49,040
It’s none of your business.

272
00:20:49,040 --> 00:20:50,880
You want to be attractive,

273
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:52,760
but you can’t.

274
00:20:53,190 --> 00:20:54,540
Nobody would like you

275
00:20:54,660 --> 00:20:57,310
other than the blind or the stupid.

276
00:20:57,700 --> 00:20:58,420
I can’t believe

277
00:20:58,420 --> 00:21:00,180
there are people like you, Chen Jinzhi.

278
00:21:00,760 --> 00:21:04,070
Did you grow up on poison?

279
00:21:04,070 --> 00:21:06,000
Yeah. I took it three times a day.

280
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:07,280
Never missed it once!

281
00:21:07,280 --> 00:21:08,880
If you don’t want to be poisoned,

282
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:09,800
then get the hell out!

283
00:21:10,800 --> 00:21:11,460
Fine.

284
00:21:12,070 --> 00:21:13,040
Mark your words.

285
00:21:15,560 --> 00:21:16,400
Wait!

286
00:21:25,880 --> 00:21:28,830
Did you buy the flowers for me?

287
00:21:29,230 --> 00:21:29,950
I...

288
00:21:30,560 --> 00:21:32,950
Why would I do that?

289
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:35,000
I’m not crazy.

290
00:21:38,830 --> 00:21:39,540
I’m leaving.

291
00:22:08,800 --> 00:22:09,560
Dawei.

