00:40:21,430 --> 00:40:22,230
Qianyu.

583
00:40:23,520 --> 00:40:24,950
You know why

584
00:40:24,950 --> 00:40:27,120
I always tell you to marry a rich man?

585
00:40:30,150 --> 00:40:32,190
To pay off Dad’s debt.

586
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:40,190
Because... I don’t want you to follow in my steps.

587
00:40:41,470 --> 00:40:43,040
I can’t do anything else

588
00:40:43,040 --> 00:40:44,430
other than running a grocery store.

589
00:40:44,800 --> 00:40:46,600
That’s why my life is hard.

590
00:40:49,280 --> 00:40:50,760
But you’re different.

591
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:54,360
You’re smart and capable.

592
00:40:54,360 --> 00:40:55,600
You belong

593
00:40:55,600 --> 00:40:57,080
to a bigger world.

594
00:40:58,230 --> 00:40:59,190
If you don’t fly,

595
00:40:59,870 --> 00:41:02,280
how do you know where your limit is?

596
00:41:03,040 --> 00:41:04,230
Don’t be afraid.

597
00:41:04,670 --> 00:41:06,080
Just go for it.

598
00:41:06,470 --> 00:41:08,760
If one day, you fall by accident,

599
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:10,600
I’ll be down there to catch you.

600
00:41:15,190 --> 00:41:16,120
Thanks, Mom.

601
00:41:18,040 --> 00:41:19,840
Be brave.

602
00:41:19,840 --> 00:41:21,470
Seize every chance coming your way.

603
00:41:22,080 --> 00:41:24,120
Every bit of it

604
00:41:24,120 --> 00:41:24,950
can make a difference.

605
00:41:25,630 --> 00:41:26,320
Understand?

606
00:41:26,910 --> 00:41:27,520
Yes.

607
00:41:29,360 --> 00:41:30,840
I’m sure you can do it.

608
00:41:31,520 --> 00:41:32,320
I can do it.

609
00:41:32,320 --> 00:41:32,860
You can do it.

610
00:41:32,860 --> 00:41:33,500
I can do it.

611
00:41:35,190 --> 00:41:36,710
I can do it.

612
00:41:36,710 --> 00:41:37,870
Think it over.

613
00:41:37,870 --> 00:41:38,390
I believe

614
00:41:38,390 --> 00:41:39,800
you’ll make the right choice.

615
00:41:46,630 --> 00:41:47,560
I’ll take it to wash.

616
00:41:50,230 --> 00:41:50,940
I can do it.

617
00:42:00,360 --> 00:42:02,230
Up to now, you still don’t trust me, do you?

618
00:42:03,190 --> 00:42:04,390
It’s your father’s talking.

619
00:42:04,390 --> 00:42:05,870
Didn’t you hear that?

620
00:42:08,040 --> 00:42:10,280
If all these couldn’t convince you…

621
00:42:10,840 --> 00:42:11,630
Xu Ziqian,

622
00:42:13,560 --> 00:42:14,950
you’re fooling yourself.

623
00:42:20,430 --> 00:42:23,430
Ziqian, your father spent all of his life on this.

624
00:42:23,910 --> 00:42:25,600
It should have been yours.

625
00:42:26,670 --> 00:42:27,800
What do you have now?

626
00:42:28,190 --> 00:42:30,630
You’re serving the Shans,

627
00:42:30,870 --> 00:42:32,760
in the name of a little director.

628
00:42:34,840 --> 00:42:36,710
I think it’s unfair.

629
00:42:38,360 --> 00:42:39,190
Tell me,

630
00:42:40,910 --> 00:42:42,950
do you still want to protect them?

631
00:43:14,900 --> 00:43:19,920
♪ Distance between us ♪

632
00:43:23,220 --> 00:43:28,310
♪ Seems short yet long ♪

633
00:43:29,370 --> 00:43:33,350
♪ Heartfelt words are exchanged in diaries ♪

634
00:43:33,370 --> 00:43:37,060
♪ There are no secrets between us ♪

635
00:43:37,610 --> 00:43:45,010
♪ Didn’t get to say I love you so much ♪

636
00:43:46,250 --> 00:43:50,550
♪ You broke into my lonely heart ♪

637
00:43:50,570 --> 00:43:54,330
♪ And lit the fire called love ♪

638
00:43:54,570 --> 00:43:58,810
♪ You drove out all my loneliness ♪

639
00:43:58,830 --> 00:44:02,340
♪ So that I can slowly adjust myself ♪

640
00:44:02,850 --> 00:44:07,010
♪ You painted my life ♪

641
00:44:07,030 --> 00:44:10,610
♪ With flowers ♪

642
00:44:10,630 --> 00:44:14,570
♪ You raised me up ♪

643
00:44:14,590 --> 00:44:17,990
♪ From that moment on ♪

644
00:44:18,520 --> 00:44:21,280
♪ You’ve been singing for me ♪

